a45&#x27;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">, {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">  size: </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">16</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">})</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">// 0x000000000000000000000000a4e12a45</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"pages/docs/utilities/pad.md#size\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nType: number\\nDefault: 32\\n\\nSize (in bytes) of the targeted value.\\npad(&#x27;0xa4e12a45&#x27;, {\\n  size: 16\\n})\\n// 0x000000000000000000000000a4e12a45\",\"title\":\"size\",\"titles\":[\"pad\",\"Parameters\"]}]}}"
